top

Load Average                                                How many processes stay in a queue
CPU:
us                                                          user spaces CPU time
sy                                                          system spaces CPU time
ni                                                          low priority process CPU time
id                                                          idle CPU time
wa                                                          i/o devices operations CPU time
hi                                                          hardware interruption CPU time
si                                                          software interruption CPU time
st                                                          stolen CPU time


top
> 1                                                         show processors

